  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Efficacy of Docetaxel and Carboplatin in Metastatic Malignant Melanoma Failed First-Line Dacabazine or Temozolomide Contained Therapy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
